    "Key issue 4: how to deal with the hyper-scale of networks?",
    "A large number of nodes can participate in distributed learning in wireless networks.",
    "This distributed collaboration can break geographical limitations and enable cross-regional cooperation.",
    "For instance, distributed learning can be deployed between devices in different provinces or cities.",
    "To organize large-scale distributed learning in the network, sites and networks must excessively coordinate; this remains a significant challenge for ensuring high collaboration efficiency and performance."
